Well as regards me father, me father was very hard working and the biggest crime in life, to me father, was to be a ly about and lazy so I always thing that - I've been able to turn to all kinds of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2823250\charrsid13856522 jobs}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522  through -
