Washed and dressed, I mean the biggest part of my childhood we were at Beswick club from me being eleven until I was twenty-one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8198053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 But when you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1468682\charrsid13856522 lived}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522  in houses how many evenings a week would your father spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13702913 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 
Well, after we - after we left the club we lived in a - a street just at the back of the club and - he'd sometimes go to the pictures during the week - but -
