\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8198053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 
He was a weaver and he was learning a different trade so it made a big drop in his wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13702913 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 Oh yes. A
nd that - ah well, he was offered this - they take the overlookers from the weavers and me father had been passed over two or three times and he was offered it and they just were quite sure he wouldn't take it because he was stuck with two little children
 and he came home and he said, I've got me chance but I can't take it. Me mother said, oh yes you can. I'll go back to work. She did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8198053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 Where did you have your meal then if your mother was at work?
