aid her but of course I don't know anything about that I was too young to know but she cooked and baked all her won bread and - it was like home to us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8198053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 This is where you used to have the hash and potato pie?
