\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13702913 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 
Well what I remember most of all was singing little songs and doing little recitations. We - we learned hang up the babies stocking. I can remember that - be sure you won't forget, for the dear little d
impled darling has never seen Christmas yet. And I told her all about it and she opened her big blue }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1468682\charrsid13856522 eyes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 , and I'm sure she understood me, she seemed so clever and wise. Yes.
