 - went alone - after being taken there. I used to take me sister because she was still in the babies when we went there. And I was only in the first class, I hadn't gone in standard one when I went there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8198053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 What did you do for your midday meal then?
