\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1195533\charrsid13856522 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 
 in for Sundays we always had curls but plaited, very - parted down the back and very tight plaits.
