Miss Boyle and - she was alive up 'til about three years ago as I know, she must have been a good age, the Headmistress but she was a real lady and she was always very, very strict on manners. Oh yes. And - she took a great interest in your position in cl
a
ss. She - she knew every girl - there was quite a lot of us because there was more than forty in a class except the top class and - before we went in for examinations we used to go in - her room, see there was only so many picked out to go in to sit for -
