t you see. Well Leah was - round about my age you see and she went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Birley Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 so - although she wasn't in my class - but we got friendly and they had a shop on this road and one in openshaw. Well sometimes they had at this shop if if was a morning or
der they might have had a coat, you see, they had a workroom in Openshaw and - we used to go - take the orders. Her mother used to give me - so I would go with her you see and she came one day and - we had to go over a recreation ground and I'd come from 
