g once time as we'd been to Ashton Palais - and me mother thought that was a - a - she thought it was a den on iniquity and - I got - she saw me get off the tram you see. I got off with a boy and of course she - what did I tell you? And she was pushing me
.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8198053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 So you had boyfriends and well as girls?
