Oh of course. Well you know you dance and they bring you home from a dance. Any - way the following week said don't take her home, her mother}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1468682\charrsid13856522 'll }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 clout you never mind her.
