Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after her house or family - relations or friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13702913 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 Well - I always remember - yes, but I always remember my mothe
r saying that when she was expecting me - and - me father's sister was also expecting a baby, they each looked after - there was three months - six months between because dies six months older than me but they looked after one another. Because they didn't
 -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8198053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 Did neighbours ever come in to help?
