d had come from another town, which town I don't know, but neighbours did her washing and looked after the other two kids. Gave them meals and did the cleaning up until she got on her feet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8198053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 Did your parents have a lot of friends and where did they see them?
