Well they were the members of the club and the wives and children because there used to be a social nearly every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8198053 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11950706\charrsid13856522 So you used to see them there?
